/** * Author(s) of this code: * * Joven Manikiza */ import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react'; import { Table, Link, Heading, Main, SectionBreak, Pagination } from 'govuk-react'; import { useNavigate } from "react-router-dom"; import Navigation from '../../Components/Navigation'; jq function Profile() { const navigate = useNavigate(); const [data, setData] = useState({}); useEffect(() => { fetch('http://localhost:4000/getData.php') .then(response => response.json()) .then(data => { setData({ fullName: data.Forename + ' ' + data.Surname, dob: data.PersonDOB, gender: data.GenderCode === '1' ? 'Male' : 'Female', address: data.Postcode, email: data.EmailAddress, contact: data.PhoneNumber }); }) .catch(error => console.error(error)); }, []); jq.ajax({ type: "POST", url: "http://localhost:4000/getData.php", mode: "no-core", xhrFields: { withCredentials: true }, success(data) { console.log(data); // process the data here }, }); return (
navigate("/Patient")} previousPage> Back to start navigate("/GPServices")} nextPage> GP Services Profile Name {data.fullName} navigate("/NameChangeStart")} children="Change"/> D.O.B {data.dob} navigate("/DOBChangeStart")} children="Change"/> Gender {data.gender} navigate("/GenderChangeStart")} children="Change"/> Address {data.address} navigate("/AddressChangeStart")} children="Change"/> Email {data.email} navigate("/EmailChangeStart")} children="Change"/> Contact No. {data.contact} navigate("/NumberChangeStart")} children="Change"/> Password ************* navigate("/PasswordChangeStart")} children="Change"/>
); } export default Profile;
